  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1599710">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1599710/" class="title-link">简体中文书里这本是关于朝鲜战争最好的</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1599710"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2583755/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2583755-25.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2583755/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">原教旨托利党人</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-12-28"
      class="main-meta">2008-12-28 16:16:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1599710_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  尽管托兰是个左翼分子，但他的书还是比较客观的讲出了一些事实，本书翻译出版时也没有删除。比如两个跳梁小丑，左翼记者魏宁顿与贝却敌的无耻行径，比如所谓“细菌弹”问题中无辜遭迫害的盟军战俘的遭遇。  客观地说，托兰这本书要比贝文.亚历山大的《朝鲜，第一次战败》好得多。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1599710/#comments">(10回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 4没用</span>
